{
  "stem": "11274.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I didn't know what they're doing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But she was screaming.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And another one was screaming.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I said, I have to see to it that I don't make that table.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So here is that other line.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So I cheated them out of this one, too.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "That other line going already to the clothes, yeah.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "From the table, perhaps, it's going to get the clothes.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Pardon me.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And-- and I slipped in there in the other row, and I didn't get to the table.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So later on, I found that they were looking for jewelry-- if they were hiding this, in every crevice in the body.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, anyway, I went without it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I went in.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I had the uniform.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "While we were picking the uniforms, we had to exchange with each other long pants.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Some of them had no buttons, the Russian uniforms-- hard buttons, big holes from the bullets in it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I didn't know where the bullets, and I didn't know from Russian uniforms.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "By the way, I'm saying Russian uniforms.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't know by that time, because there were no insignia on it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I didn't know that they were.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I found out later that they were Russian uniforms.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because in '41, Germany attacked Russia, and they took prisoners of war, OK?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we had those uniforms.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And no underwear, nothing at all.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Just the uniforms with the holes and with the lice in it because there were already for months there, for a whole year, I think.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And a piece of wood, for-- different sizes of wood with a leather strip.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that was all the clothes that we got.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And with that clothes, we went.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "After we were processed, everybody was ready.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They put, like, 80 of us in-- in one room, or maybe more.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
